Package javelin.model.world.place.town.research

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AccommodationResearch
    Allows a Town to upgrade it's Town.lodging.
    Discard
    For 1 labor allows player to discard one option from Town#research.researchhand.
    Grow
    Grows Town.size by 1.
    ItemResearch
    Allows a new native or foreign (double cost) item to be sold in this Town.
    LairResearch
    Allows a new Monster to be recruited in this town.
    Recruit
    This is a special research card that allows hostile towns to generate units.
    Redraw
    For 2 labor allows player to redraw all options from Town#research.researchhand.
    Research
    Represents a way in which a Town can be improved.
    SpecialResearchCard
    These are supposed to be a stack of research cards each with a unique effect.
    TransportResearch
    Allows for upgrading Town.transport.
    UpgradeResearch
    Allows a new native (1 labor) or foreign (2 labor) Upgrade to be trained in this town.
